'''Sirta''' tga tamaẓunt n tgldit tamaziɣt n Numidya. Aftas nns astratiji iga t [[Rusikada]]. Tlla ɣ lqblt n tmazirt n [[Dzayr]]. Waxxa Numidya tga tamẓṭṭiḍt n tgduda n ṛuma ɣ uzmz n uqryan abuniqi (-264 ar -146), hjmn fllas iṛumiyn aylliɣ tkcm ddu tnbaḍt n ṛuma ɣ uzmz n Yulyus Qaysar. 

Ibna tt Qusṭanṭin Amqran ɣ usggʷas 312 s umaynu, ismmu as '''Qusṭanṭina'''.

